Challenge 28: Merge Intervals
What to do:
Given a list of intervals, merge all overlapping intervals and return the result.
Example Input:
intervals = [[1,3],[2,6],[8,10],[15,18]]
Example Output:
[[1,6],[8,10],[15,18]]
Explanation:
The intervals [1,3] and [2,6] overlap, so they are merged into [1,6].
